hadiths[153]{hadithnumber,text}:
1956,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Ramazan aata hai to aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' jannat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur jahannam ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur shayatin ko jakad diya jata hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' rehmat ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1957,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat ke aath darwazey hain, un mein se eik darwazey ka naam '' Rayyan'' hai, is mein se sirf roza daar hi dakhil hongey .'' muttafaq aleh."
1958,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs eman w ikhlas aur sawab ki niyat se rozey rakhey to uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, jo shakhs eman w ikhlas aur sawab ki niyat se Ramazan mein qiyam karey ( Namaz tarawih ka ehtimam karey ( to uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain, aur jo shakhs eman w ikhlas aur sawab ki niyat se shabe-qadr ka qiyam karey to uskey sabiqa gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
1959,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ibne-Adam ke her nek amal ko das guna se saat so guna tak badha diya jata hai, Allah Taala farmata hai : rozey ke siwa , kyonkey wo merey liye hai aur main hi uski jaza dunga, wo apni khahish aur apney khaney ko meri wajeh se tarak karta hai. roza daar ke liye do khushiyan hain, eik farhat w khushi to uskey iftaar ke waqt hai jabkey eik khushi apney rab se mulaqat ke waqt hai, aur roza daar ke munh ki bo Allah ke yahan kastoori ki khushbu se bhi ziyada behtar hai, aur roza dhaal hai, jis roz tum mein se kisi ka roza ho to wo fohsh goi aur hiziyaan se ijtinab karey, agar koi usey bura bhala kahey ya us se ladaai jhagda karey to wo kahey ke main roza daar hun.'' muttafaq aleh."
1960,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Ramazan ki pehli raat hoti hai to shayatin aur sarkash jinnon ko jakad diya jata hai, jahannam ke tamam darwazey band kar diye jatey hain un mein se koi darwaza nahin khola jata, aur jannat ke tamam darwazey khol diye jatey hain aur un mein se koi darwaza band nahin kiya jata, aur manadi karney wala aelan karta hai : khair aur bhalai ke Talib ! aagey badh , aur shar ke Talib ! ruk ja , aur Allah ke liye jahannam se azad karda log hain, aur her raat aisey hota hai.''"
1961,"aur Imam Ahmed ne usey kisi sahabi se riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
1962,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maahe-mubarak Ramazan tumharey paas aaya hai, Allah ne uska roza tum par farz kya hai, is mein aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain, jahannam ke darwazey band kar diye jatey hain aur sarkash shayatin band kar diye jatey hain, us ( maah ( main eik raat hazar mahinon se behtar hai, jo shakhs uski khair w bhalai se mehroom kar diya gaya to wo ( her khair w bhalai sey) mehroom kar diya gaya .'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai ."
1963,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' roza aur Quran bandey ke liye sifarish karengey , roza arz kerega, rab ji ! maine din ke waqt khaney peeney aur khaahishat se usey rok rakha , uskey mutalliq meri sifarish qubul farma aur Quran arz kerega : maine usey raat ke waqt soney se rokey rakha , uskey mutalliq meri sifarish qubul farma , un dono ki sifarish qubul ki jaeygi .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
1964,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Ramazan aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye mahina jo tumharey paas aaya hai us main eik raat hai jo ke hazar mahinon se behtar hai, aur jo shakhs us se mehroom kar diya gaya to wo her qism ki khair w bhalai se mehroom kar diya gaya aur uski khair se mehroom shakhs her qism ki khair w bhalai se mehroom hai.''"
1965,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Shoban ke aakhiri roz hamen khitab kartey huey farmaya : '' logo ! eik ba barkat maahe-azeem tum par saya-figan hua hai, us main eik raat hazar mahinon se behtar hai, Allah ne uska roza farz aur raat ka qiyam nafl qarar diya hai, jisney is mein koi nafl kaam kya to wo uskey ilawa baqi mahinon mein farz ada karney waley ki tarah hai aur jisney is mein farz ada kya to wo us shakhs ki tarah hai jisney uskey ilawa mahinon mein sattar farz ada kiye, wo maahe-sabr hai jabke sabr ka sawab jannat hai, wo gham gusari ka mahina hai, is mein momin ka rizq badha diya jata hai, jo is mein kisi roze daar ko iftaarii kiraaey to wo uskey gunahon ki maghfirat ka aur jahannam se azadi ka sabab hogi aur usey bhi us (roze daar) ki misl sawab milta hai aur uskey ajr mein koi kami nahin ki jati.'' ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham sab ye istataat nahin rakhtey ke ham roze daar ko iftaari karaein, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ye sawab us shakhs ko bhi ata farma deta hai jo lassi ke ghoont ya eik khajoor ya pani ke eik ghoont se kisi roze daar ki iftaari karata hai aur jo shakhs kisi roze daar ko pet bharkar deta hai to Allah usey merey hoz se (pani) pilaeyga to usey jannat mein dakhil ho janey tak piyas nahin lagegi aur wo aisa mahina hai jis ka awwal (ashra) rehmat , uska wast maghfirat aur uska aakhir jahannam se khulaasi hai, aur jo shakhs is mein apney mamlook se riayat bartega to Allah uski maghfirat farma dega aur usey jahannam se azad kar dega.''"
1966,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab maah Ramazan aata to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her qaidi ko azad farma detey aur her saail ko ata kya kartey they."
1967,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jannat ko Ramazan ke liye pura saal muzayyan kya jata hai.'' farmaya : ''jab Ramazan ka pehla din hota hai to arsh ke nichey jannat ke patton se hawa chalti hui hoore-ain tak pahunchti hai to wo kehti hain : rab ji ! apney bandon mein se hamarey shohar bana dey, ham un se apni aankhen thandi karen aur wo ham se apni aankhen thandi keren.'' Imam Behaqi ne teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain."
1968,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ramazan ki aakhiri raat unki (yani meri) ummat ko bakhsh diya jata hai.''arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo shabe-qadr hai? farmaya : '' nahin, lekin jab kaam karney wala apna kaam mukammal kar leta hai to usey pura pura ajr diya jata hai.''"
1969,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum roza na rakho yahan tak ke tum ( Ramazan ka ( chaand dekh lo aur roza rakhna moquf na karo yahan tak ke tum us ( Hilal shawwal ( ko dekh lo , agar matla abr aalud ho to uskey liye ( tees din ka ( andaza kar lo .'' aur eik riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''maah untees din ka bhi hota hai, tum roza na rakho yahan tak ke tum us ( Hilal Ramazan ( ko dekh lo , agar matla abr aalud ho to phir tees ki ginti mukammal kar lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
1970,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us (Hilal Ramazan) ke dekhney par roza rakho aur us (Hilal shawwaal) ke dekhney par roza rakhna chhod do aur agar matla abr aalud ho to phir Shoban ki ginti tees tak mukammal kar lo .'' muttafaq aleh."
1971,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak ham ُ ummi ( likhney padhney se naa-balad ( log hain, ham hisab kitab nahin jantey, mahina is tarah aur is tarah aur is tarah hota hai.'' teesri martaba aapney angoothey ko band kar liya , phir farmaya : '' mahina is tarah, is tarah aur is tarah hota hai.'' yani mukammal tees, yani aapney eik martaba untees aur eik martaba tees ka zikr kya. muttafaq aleh."
1972,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eid ke do mahiney , Ramazan aur zul-hijja , kam nahin hotey .'' muttafaq aleh."
1973,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs Ramazan se eik ya do din pehley roza na rakhey, albatta agar koi shakhs mamool se rozey rakhta chala aa raha hai to wo us roz roza rakh ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
1974,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab nisf Shoban ho jaey to phir roza na rakho .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
1975,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ramazan ki khatir Shoban ke chaand (dinon) ki ginti karo.''"
1976,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Shoban ke ilawa do maah lagataar rozey rakhtey huey nahin dekha. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
1977,Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain jis shakhs ne shak ke din ka roza rakha to usney abul-Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki .
1978,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehati) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney kaha : maine Ramazan ka chaand dekha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain ?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Bilal ! logon mein aelan kar do ke wo kal roza rakhen.''"
1979,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain log chaand dekhney ke liye jama huey to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya ke maine usko dekh liya hai, aapney roza rakha aur logon ko bhi roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1980,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Shoban ki ginti ka deegar mahinon ki nisbat ziyada ehtimam kiya kartey they, phir aap Ramazan ka chaand nazar aaney par roza rakhtay, agar aasman mein baadal hota to aap tees din ki ginti farmatey phir roza rakhtay. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1981,"Hazrat Abul-Bakhtari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Umre ke liye rawana huye, jab ham ne batan nakhla ke maqam par padaaw dala to ham chaand dekhney ke liye ikhattey huye, to kuchh logon ne kaha : ye teesri raat ka hai, kisi ne kaha : dusri raat ka hai, ham ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se miley to ham ne kaha : ham ne chaand dekha to kisi ne kaha : wo teesri raat ka hai aur kisi ne kaha : dusri raat ka hai, unhoney farmaya : tum ne kis raat usey dekha tha? ham ne kaha : falan falan raat , unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is (Ramazan) ki muddat uske chaand dekhne par muqarrar ki hai, wo (Ramazan) us raat se shuru hota hai jis raat tum usey dekho. aur Abul-Bakhtari (Raziallahu anhu) ki eik dusri riwayat mein hai : unhoney kaha : ham ne zaat arq ke maqam par Ramazan ka chaand dekha, to ham ne masla daryaft karney ke liye eik aadmi ko ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja to unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne is (Shoban) ko is (Hilal Ramazan) ka chaand dekhne tak daraz kiya hai, agar aasman par badal ho to ginti ko mukammal kar lo.'' rawahu Muslim."
1982,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sehri khaya karo kyonkey sehri khaney mein barkat hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1983,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey aur ehle-kitab ke rozon mein sehri khaney ka farq hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
1984,"Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak log iftaari karney mein jaldi kartey rahengey wo khair aur bhalai par rahengey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1985,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab raat is taraf se aa jaey aur din is taraf palat jaey aur Suraj ghurub ho jaey to roze daar ko chahiye ke wo iftaar karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
1986,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rozon mein wisaal karney se mana farmaya , to kisi aadmi ne aap se arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap to wisaal farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kon meri tarah hai? main raat ko sota hun to mera rab mujhey khila pila deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
1987,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs tulu Fajr se pehley rozey ki niyat na karey to uska roza nahin.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , Darmi aur Abu-Dawood ne farmaya : Maamer , Zubaidi, ibne-Uena aur Yunus illi ne is hadees ko Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) par moquf qarar diya hai aur in sab ne Zohri se riwayat kiya hai."
1988,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Azan (Fajr) suney aur (khaney peeney ka ( bartan uskey haath mein ho to wo apni zarurat puri karney ke baad usey nichey rakhey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1989,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : mujhey apney wo bandey ziyada mehbub hain jo un mein se iftaar karney mein jaldi kartey hain.''"
1990,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi iftaar karey to wo khajoor se iftaar karey kyonkey wo baaise-barkat hai, agar wo na paey to phir pani se iftaar kar ley kyonkey wo baaise-tahaarat (paakizgi) hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi , lekin unhoney ye nahin kaha : ''kyonkey wo baaise-barkat hai.'' sirf Imam Tirmizi ne ye alfaz eik dusri riwayat se naqal kiye hain. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
1991,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz (maghrib) padhney se pehley chand taza khajuron se iftaar kiya kartey they, agar taza khajuren na hotin to phir chand chhuwaron se aur agar chhuhaarey na hotey to phir pani ke chand ghoont pi liya kartey they. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
1992,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi roze-daar ka roza iftaar kiraaey ya kisi Mujahid ki tayyari kara dey to usey bhi us (roze-daar ya Mujahid) ke jaisa ajr milta hai.'' (Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) . aur Mughi Usunna ne Sharahus-Sunnah mein riwayat kiya aur unhoney kaha ye riwayat sahih hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
1993,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roza iftaar kartey to aap ye dua padha kartey they : ''piyas jati rahi , ragein tar hogaeen aur agar Allah ne chaha to ajr Sabit ho gaya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1994,Hazrat Muaz bin Zohra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab iftaar kartey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua padha kartey they : ''aey Allah ! maine terey hi liye roza rakha aur terey hi rizq se iftaar kiya.'' Abu-Dawood ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai.
1995,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak log iftaar karney mein jaldi kartey rahengey Deen ghalib rahega kyonkey yahood aur Nasara (iftaar karney mein) takheer (deri) kartey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
1996,"Hazrat Abu Atiyaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur Masruq , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to ham ne arz kiya : Ummul-momenin ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se do aadmi hain un mein se eik jaldi iftaar kartey hain aur jald hi Namaz (maghrib) padhtey hain, jabkey doosrey der se iftaar kartey hain aur der se Namaz padhtey hain, unhoney farmaya : un mein se kon jald iftaar karta hai aur jald Namaz padhta hai? ham ne arz kiya Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) , unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bhi aisey hi kiya, jabkey doosrey Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) hain. rawahu Muslim."
1997,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ramazan mein mujhey sehri ki dawat detey huey farmaya : ''mubarak khaney ki taraf aao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
1998,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ki behtareen sehri khajoor hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
1999,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs (roze ki haalat mein) jhoot aur burey aamaal tarak nahin karta to Allah ko koi hajat (zaroorat) nahin ke wo shakhs apna khana peena tarak kar dey.'' Bukhari ."
2000,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roze ki haalat mein bosa ley liya kartey they aur galey mil liya kartey they aur aap apni khahish par tum se ziyada qabu rakhney waley they. muttafaq aleh."
2001,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Ramazan mein kabhi jima (sambhog) ki wajeh se haalate-janabat mein subah ho jati to aap ghusl kartey aur phir roza rakhtay. muttafaq aleh."
2002,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehram aur roze ki haalat mein pachhney lagwaaey. muttafaq aleh.
2003,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bhool jaey ke wo roze se hai aur wo kha ley ya pi ley to wo apna roza pura karey kyonkey usey to Allah ne khilaya pilaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2004,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke itney main eik aadmi ne aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main to maara gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kya hua?'' usney arz kiya : main rozey ki haalat main apni ehliya se jima (sambhog) kar betha hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas koi ghulam hai jisey to azad kar dey?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum lagataar do maah rozey rakh saktey ho?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum saath miskinon ko khana khila saktey ho?'' usney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beth jaao.'' isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne twaqquf farmaya (thehra liya), ham isi beech mein they ke khajuron ka eik bada tokraa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''masla daryaft karney wala kahan hai? '' us shakhs ne arz kiya, main hazir hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye lo isey sadqa kar do.'' us aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya main apney se ziyada mohtaj shakhs par sadqa karun? Allah ki qism ! (Madina mein) do pathreeley kinaron ke darmiyan koi aisa ghar nahin jo merey ghar walon se ziyada zarurat mand ho, (ye sun kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is qadr hansay ke aap ke daant Mubarak zahir ho gaey, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey apney ghar walon ko khilao.'' muttafaq aleh."
2005,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) roze ki haalat mein kabhi unka bosa ley liya kartey they aur unki zaban choos liya kartey they.
2006,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kisi aadmi ne , roze daar ke liye apni ehliya se galey milney ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aapney usey rukhsat (chhoot) inayat farma di, phir eik aur aadmi aaya aur usney aap se masla puchha to aapney usey rok diya, jis shakhs ko rukhsat inayat farmaai thi wo boodha aadmi tha aur jisey rok diya tha wo eik no-jawan shakhs tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2007,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko roze ki haalat mein qai aa jaey to is par koi qaza nahin aur jo shakhs amadan qai karey to wo (roze ki) qaza karey.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , Darmi aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai, ham Esa bin Yunus se marwi (bayan) hadees ke hawaley se hi isey jantey hain, jabkey Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari ne farmaya : main isey mehfooz nahin samajhta."
2008,"Hazrat Maadaan bin Talha se riwayat hai ke Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qai ki to aapney roza iftaar kar liya, raawi bayan kartey hain, main dimashq ki masjid mein Soban se mila to maine kaha ke Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadees bayan ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qai ki to aapney roza iftaar kar liya , unhoney kaha : unhon (yani abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu)) ne theek kaha hai, aur maine aap ke liye aap ke wuzu ka pani undela tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi aur Darmi."
2009,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine un-ginat martaba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko roza ki haalat mein miswak kartey huey dekha hai."
2010,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : mujhey aashoob chashm (aankh dukhna ya aankh ki takleef) hai kya main roze ki haalat mein surma dal lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' Tirmizi aur unhoney farmaya : iski sanad qawi nahin, Abu Aatiqa raawi zaeef hai."
2011,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : maine maqame-araj par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haalate-roze mein piyas ya garmi ki wajeh se sar par pani daltey huey dekha. rawahu Malik aur Abu-Dawood."
2012,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baqee main eik aadmi ke paas se guzrey jabke wo pachhney lagwa raha tha, aap mera haath thaamey huey they aur Ramazan ki atthaara taareekh thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pachhney laganey aur lagwaaney waley ka roza toot gay .'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja, Darmi. al-Sheikh Imam Muhiussunnah ne farmaya : aur jin baaz hazraat ne roze ki haalat mein pachhney lagwaaney ki ijazat di hai, unhoney ye taaweel ki hai ke pachhney lagwaaney wala kamzori ki wajeh se iftaar ke qarib pahunch jata hai, jabke pachhney laganey wala us choosney ki wajeh se pet mein koi chiz pahunchney se bach nahin sakta. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2013,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi rukhsat (safar waghera) aur marz ke baghair Ramazan ka eik roza chhod dey to phir agar wo puri zindagi rozey rakhta rahey to wo us eik din ke rozey ke ajr w sawab ko nahin pa sakta.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , Darmi aur Imam Bukhari ne (ترجمۃ الباب) mein riwayat kiya hai aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : maine Muhammad yani Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna : main Abul Mutwwis ko is hadees ke ilawa nahin janta ke usney koi aur hadees bhi riwayat ki ho."
2014,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kitney hi roze daar hain jinhen apney roze se sirf piyas hasil hoti hai aur kitney hi qiyam karney waley hain jinhen apney qiyam se jaagney ke siwa kuchh hasil nahin hota.'' Darmi , aur Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees , sunun wuzu ke bayan mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Darmi."
2015,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen chizen roza nahin todtin, pachhney, qai aur ehtilaam.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees mehfooz nahin, Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid raawi, hadees mein zaeef hai."
2016,"Hazrat Sabit Bunani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein roze-daar ke pachhney laganey ko na pasand kiya kartey they? unhoney farmaya : nahin, sirf kamzori ke peshe-nazar. Bukhari."
2017,"Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) se muallaq riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) roze ki haalat mein pachhney lagwaayaa kartey they, phir usey tarak kar diya, phir aap raat ke waqt pachhney lagwate they. Bukhari."
2018,"Hazrat Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, agar kulli karey, phir munh ke pani ko gira dey to phir agar wo apna thook aur jo pani uskey munh mein baqi reh gaya tha nigal ley to uskey liye Muzar nahin, albatta wo gond na chabaey , agar wo gond ka luaab nigal ley to main nahin kehta ke wo roza tod lega, lekin usey us se roka jaeyga. Imam Bukhari ne isey (ترجمعۃ الباب) mein riwayat kiya hai. Bukhari."
2019,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) bahut ziyada rozey rakha kartey they, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya : kya main dorane-safar roza rakh liya karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to roza rakho aur agar tum chaho to na rakho.'' muttafaq aleh."
2020,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne sola Ramazan ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein jihad kiya, ham mein se kuchh ne roza rakha hua tha aur kuchh ne roza nahin rakha hua tha, roze daar ne roze na rakhney waley ko  (aibdar) samjha na iftaar karney waley ne roza daar ko (aibdar) samjha. rawahu Muslim."
2021,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar mein they ke aapney hujoom aur eik aadmi dekha jis par saya kiya hua hai to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kya hua?'' Sahaba ne arz kiya : roza daar hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safar mein roza rakhna koi neki nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
2022,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shareeke-safar they, ham mein se kuchh rozey se they aur kuchh ne roza nahin rakha hua tha, eik sakht garm din mein ham ne eik jagah padaaw dala to roze daar to (nidhaal ho kar) gir padey , jabkey jin logon ne roza nahin rakha hua tha wo khadey huey aur unhoney khemey lagaey aur sawaariyon ko pani pilaya , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj roza na rakhney waley ajr ley gaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2023,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina se Makka ke liye rawana huey to aapney roza rakha , yahan tak ke aap maqam Asfan par pahunchey to aapney pani mangaayaa aur usey haath se buland kiya taake log usey dekh lein, isliye aapney roza iftaar kar liya yahan tak ke aap Makka pahunch gaey aur ye Ramazan ka waqia hai, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) farmaya kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (dorane-safar) roza rakha bhi hai aur iftaar bhi kiya hai, jo chahey roza rakhey aur jo chahey na rakhey. muttafaq aleh."
2024,Hazrat Sahih Muslim mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai ke aapney Asr ke baad (pani) piya. rawahu Muslim.
2025,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik Ka'bi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne musafir se nisf (aadhi) Namaz saaqit (khatam) farma di jabkey musafir, doodh pilaney wali aur hamila khatoon se roza saaqit (khatam) farma diya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2026,"Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas sawari ho jo uska pet bhar dey wo rozey rakhey jahan bhi wo Ramazan ko pa ley.''"
2027,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka ke saal Ramazan main Makka ke liye rawana huey to aapney roza rakha , yahan tak ke aap maqame-kuraal Ghameem par pahunchey , Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi roza rakha hua tha, phir aapney pani ka piyala mangwaya , usey buland kiya yahan tak ke Sahaba kiram ne usey dekh liya , phir aapney usey nosh farmaya, uskey baad aap ko bataya gaya ke baaz logon ne roza rakha hua hai (abhi tak iftaar nahin kiya) to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo nafarman hain, wo nafarman hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
2028,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dorane-safar Ramazan ka roza rakhney wala, haalate-qiyam mein roza na rakhney waley ki tarah hai.''"
2029,"Hazrat Hamza bin Amr Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main dorane-safar roza rakhney ki quwat rakhta hun, to kya (dorane safar roza rakhney par) mujhey gunah hoga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo Shan Wale Allah ki taraf se eik rukhsat hai, jisney usey ley liya to usney achchaa kiya aur jo shakhs roza rakhna chahey to is par koi gunah nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
2030,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, mujh par Ramazan ke rozey hotey to main sirf Shoban mein unki qaza dey sakti thi. Yahya bin Saeed bayan kartey hain, unki murad ye hai ke (qaza mein takheer) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mashghooliyat ki wajeh se thi. muttafaq aleh."
2031,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi aurat ke liye , apney khawind ke paas hotey huey uski ijazat ke baghair nafli roza rakhna jayez nahin, aur wo uski ijazat ke baghair kisi ko uskey ghar mein aaney ki ijazat na dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2032,Hazrat Muaza Adwiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kiya : haaiza ka kya maamla hai ke wo roze ki qaza deti hai aur Namaz ki qaza nahin deti? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : ham bhi is se dochaar hoti thin to hamen rozey ki qaza ka hukm diya jata tha jabkey Namaz ki qaza ka hukm nahin diya jata tha. rawahu Muslim.
2033,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur uskey zimme rozey hon to uski taraf se uska waris rozey rakhega.'' muttafaq aleh."
2034,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur uskey zimme maahe-Ramazan ke rozey hon to uski taraf se her rozey ke badley eik miskeen ko khana khilaya jaey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : durust baat ye hai ke ye Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf hai."
2035,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain, unhen ye khabar pahunchi hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se masla puchha gaya tha, kya koi shakhs kisi doosrey ki taraf se roza rakh sakta hai ya koi kisi doosrey shakhs ki taraf se Namaz padh sakta hai? unhoney farmaya : '' koi kisi ki taraf se roza rakh sakta hai na koi kisi ki taraf se Namaz padh sakta hai.''"
2036,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nafli rozey (musalsal) rakhtey rehtey yahan tak ke ham kahtin ke aap roza rakhna tarak nahin karengey , aur aap roza rakhna tarak farma detey yahan tak ke ham kahtin ke aap roze nahin rakhengey , aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maahe-Ramazan ke siwa kisi aur mahiney ke mukammal rozey rakhtey huey nahin dekha . aur maine aap ko Shoban ke ilawa kisi aur maah mein ziyada rozey rakhtey huey nahin dekha . eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap bayan karti hain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pura Shoban rozey rakha kartey they, aur aap Shoban mein ziyada rozey rakha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
2037,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Shafiq bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pura mahina rozey rakha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : main aap ke barey mein nahin jaanti ke aapney Ramazan ke ilawa kisi maah ke purey rozey rakhey hon, aur aisey bhi nahin ke aapney kisi maah mein koi roza na rakha ho balke aap her maah kuch rozey rakhtey they yahan tak ke aap wafat pa gaey. rawahu Muslim."
2038,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney us (yani mujh) se ya kisi aadmi se puchha jabkey Imran sun raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu falan ! kya tum ne Shoban ke aakhir ke rozey nahin rakhey?'' usney arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum (Ramazan ke) rozey rakhna chhod do to phir do din ke rozey rakh lena.'' muttafaq aleh."
2039,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ramazan ke baad Allah ke mahiney mohrram ka roza behtareen roza hai, aur farz Namaz ke baad raat ki Namaz (yani tahajjud) behtareen Namaz hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2040,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us din aashoora ke din aur us maah yani maahe Ramazan ke rozon ke siwa kisi aur din aur kisi aur maah ke rozey ka ehtimam kartey huey nahin dekha aur aapney us ( aashoora ke) din ko baqi dinon (dinon) par fazilat di. muttafaq aleh."
2041,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aashoora ka roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya to unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye to wo din hai ke yahood aur Nasara uski tazeem kartey hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mein aainda saal tak zinda raha to main naween (mohrram) ka (bhi) roza rakhunga.'' rawahu Muslim."
2042,"Hazrat Umme-Fazal binte Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kuchh logon ne Arfa ke din unke yahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rozey ke barey mein ikhtilaf kiya to kuchh ne kaha : aap roze se hain, aur kuchh ne kaha ke aap roze se nahin hain, maine doodh ka piyala aap ki khidmat mein bheja , aap maidane Arafat mein apney oont par Sawar they, to aapney usey nosh farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
2043,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko (zul-hijja ke) ushra mein kabhi rozey se nahin dekha. rawahu Muslim."
2044,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney puchha : aap roze kaisey rakhtey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski baat se naraz huey : jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki narazi dekhi to kaha : ham Allah ke rab honey , Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Nabi honey par razi hain, ham Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki narazi se Allah ki panah chahtey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) bar-bar ye baat dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ghussa jata raha to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! us shakhs ki kya haalat hai jo hamesha rozey rakhta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney roza rakha na iftaar kiya.'' phir unhoney arz kiya is shakhs ka kya haal hai jo do din roza rakhta hai aur eik din nahin rakhta? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi uski taqat rakhta hai.'' phir unhoney arz kiya : uska kya haal hai jo eik din roza rakhta hai aur eik din nahin rakhta? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza hai.'' aur phir unhoney arz kiya is shakhs ka kya haal hai jo eik din roza rakhta hai aur do din nahin rakhta? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main chahta hun ke mujhey iski taqat mil jaey, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her maah (beez ke dinon ke) teen rozey aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna ye hamesha roze rakhney ke jaisa hai jabkey yoam Arfa (9-zul-hijja) ke rozey ke barey mein Allah se ummid karta hun ke wo sabiqa aur aainda saal ke gunah mita dega aur yoame aashoora ke roze ke barey mein main Allah se ummid karta hun ke wo sabiqa saal ke gunah mita dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
2045,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se peer ke roze ke barey mein puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : '' yehi mera yoame-paidaish hai aur yehi yoame-nabuwat (yani isi roz mujh par wahi nazil ki gaee).'' rawahu Muslim."
2046,"Hazrat Muaza Adwiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwaayat hai ke unhoney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her maah teen din roza rakha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : haan , phir maine un se puchha : aap mahiney ke kon se dinon (din) roza rakha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap is baat ki parwah nahin kiya kartey they ke aap mahiney ke kin dinon (dinon) mein roza rakhengey. rawahu Muslim."
2047,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Ramazan ke rozey rakhey , phir uskey baad shawwaal ke chhe rozey rakhey to goya usney zamane bhar ke (musalsal) rozey rakhey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2048,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha ke din roza rakhney se mana farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
2049,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eidul-fitr aur eidul-azha ke do dinon (dinon) mein roza rakhna jayez nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
2050,"Hazrat Nabeesha Hazli (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ayyaame-tashreeq (11, 12, 13 zul-hijja) khaney peeney aur Allah ka zikr karney ke din hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
2051,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi sirf Jume ke din roza na rakhey, ye ke wo us se pehley ya uskey baad roza rakhey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2052,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum raaton mein se sirf Jume ki raat ko qiyam ke liye khas karo na dino mein se Jume ke din ko roze ke liye khas karo siwaey iske ke wo (Jume ka din) tum mein se kisi ke roze rakhney ke dinon (dinon) mein aa jaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2053,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs dorane jihad eik din roza rakhta hai to Allah us shakhs ko sattar saal ki masafat (doori) ke barabar jahannam se door kar deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2054,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''Abdullah ! mujhey bataya gaya hai ke tum din ko roza rakhtey ho aur raat ko qiyam kartey ho?'' maine arz kiya, ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey na kiya kar, roza rakha kar aur kabhi na bhi rakha kar , raat ko qiyam bhi kiya kar aur soyaa bhi kar , kyonkey terey jism ka tujh par haq hai, teri aankh ka tujh par haq hai, teri ehliya ka tujh par haq hai aur terey mehman ka tujh par haq hai, musalsal rozey rakhney waley ka koi roza nahin, her maah teen din rozey rakhna , zamana bhar ke rozey rakhney ke mutraadif (barabar) hai, her mahiney teen rozey rakha kar aur her maah Quran Majeed mukammal kiya kar.'' maine arz kiya, main is se ziyada ki taqat rakhta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen rozey rakh , Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey , eik din roza aur eik din iftaar. saat din mein Quran Majeed mukammal kar , aur is par izafa na kar.'' muttafaq aleh."
2055,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pair aur Jumerat ke din roza rakha kartey they. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
2056,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''peer aur Jumerat ke roz aamaal pesh kiye jatey hain, lihaza main pasand karta hun ke mera amal is haal mein pesh kya jaey ke main rozey se hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2057,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey abu-Zar! jab tum mahiney mein teen rozey rakho to tera, chaudah, aur pandarah ka roza rakho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
2058,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her maah ke shuru mein teen rozey rakha kartey they aur aap kam hi Juma ke din roza chhoda kartey they. Tirmizi, Nasai aur Abu-Dawood ne teen din tak riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w Abu-Dawood ."
2059,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi maah hafta, itwaar aur peer ka roza rakhtey to doosrey maah mangal, buddh aur Jumerat ka roza rakhtey they."
2060,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey hukm farmaya kartey they ke main her maah teen rozey rakhun, unki ibtida (shuruat) peer se ho ya Jumerat se .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2061,"Hazrat Muslim qarshii (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha ya aap se hamesha roza rakhney ke mutalliq masla puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak terey ghar walon ka tujh par haq hai, Ramazan aur uskey sath waley maah aur her buddh , Jumerat ka roza rakha kar , ( agar tum ne aisey kar liya ( to tum ne ( hukman ( zamana bhar ke rozey rakhey .''"
2062,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Arfa (no zul-hijja) ke din maidan Arafat mein roza rakhney se mana farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
2063,"Hazrat Abdullah bin basar apni behan Samma se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hafta ke din roza na rakho siwaey iske ke us roz aur koi aisa roza aa jaey jo tum par farz kya gaya hai, agar tum mein se koi angoor ka chhilka ya kisi darkht ki lakdi ke maa-siwa kuch na paey to usey hi chabaa ley.'' (taake sirf hafta ka roza Sabit na ho ( . rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2064,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raahe-jihad main eik roza rakhta hai to Allah uskey aur jahannam ke beech zamin w aasman ki masafat jitni eik khandaq bana deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
2065,"Hazrat Aamir bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sardi mein roza thandi ghanimat hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees mursal hai."
2066,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ما من ایام احب الی اللہ baab الاضحیۃ ( mein zikr ki gaee hai.
2067,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to aapney yahudiyon ko yoam Aashoora ka roza rakhtey huey paya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un se puchha : ''ye kon sa din hai jiska tum roza rakhtey ho?'' unhoney arz kya, ye eik azeem din hai, Allah ne us roz Musa (Alaihissalam) aur unki qom ko najat di jabkey Firon aur uski qom ko gharq kya to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne shukr ke taur par us din ka roza rakha to ham bhi us roz ka roza rakhtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham tumhari nisbat Musa (Alaihissalam) ke ziyada haq daar hain.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us roz ka roza rakha aur uska roza rakhney ka hukm farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
2068,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada tar hafta aur itwaar ke din roza rakha kartey they, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''ye dono mushrekin ke dinon eid hain, lihaza mein unki mukhalifat karna pasand karta hun.'' iski sanadHasan hai, rawahu Ahmed ."
2069,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Aashoora key din ka roza rakhney ka hamen hukm farmaya kartey they, uski hamen targheeb diya kartey they aur uskey mutalliq hamen nasihat farmaya kartey they, jab Ramazan farz kya gaya to aapney uskey mutalliq hamen hukm farmaya na mana kya aur na hi hamen uskey mutalliq nasihat farmatey. rawahu Muslim."
2070,"Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, chaar umur (batein) hain jinhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tarak nahin kya kartey they : yoame-Aashoora ka roza, zul-hijja ke das rozey, her maah teen rozey aur Fajr se pehley do rakatein."
2071,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hazar w safar mein beez dey dinon (tera, chaudah aur pandarah taareekh) ka roza nahin chhodtey they. rawahu Nasai ."
2072,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her chiz ki Zakat hai jabkey jism ki Zakat roza hai.'' ."
2073,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) peer aur Jumerat ka roza rakha kartey they, aap se arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap peer aur Jumerat ka roza rakhtey hain, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak peer aur Jumerat ke roz Allah baham (aapas mein) qata talluq karney waley do aadmiyon ke siwa her musalman ko bakhsh deta hai aur wo farmata hai : un dono ko chhod do yahan tak ke wo dono suleh kar lein.'' rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja."
2074,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raza ki khatir eik roza rakhta hai to Allah usey jahannam se is qadr door farma deta hai jaisey eik udney wala kawwa bachpan ki umr se udna shuru karey aur boodha honey tak udta rahey yahan tak ke wo faut ho jaey.'' (wo sari zindagi mein jitna fasla tey karta hai Allah us shakhs ko itni masafat jahannam se door kar deta hai) ."
2075,Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne isey Salma bin Qais se Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kya hai.
2076,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik roz merey paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas ( khaney ke liye ( koi chiz hai? '' ham ne arz kya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main phir roze se hun.'' phir aap kisi roz hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! hamen hees ( khajoor , ghi aur paneer se tayyar karda halwa ( hadiya kya gaya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey dikhaao, maine subh roza rakha hua tha.'' aapney (usey) kha liya . rawahu Muslim ."
2077,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif laye to unhoney khajoor aur ghi aap ki khidmat mein pesh kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghi aur khajuren wapis unke bartan mein dal do kyonkey main roze se hun.'' phir aap khadey huey aur ghar ke eik koney mein nafl Namaz ada ki aur umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke ehle khana ke liye dua farmatey . Bukhari ."
2078,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney ki dawat di jaey jabkey wo roze se ho to wo kahey : ''main roza se hun.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko dawat di jaey to wo qubul karey, agar wo rozey se ho to wo dua karey aur agar rozey se na ho to khana kha ley.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2079,"Hazrat Umme- Hani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, jab Fateh Makka ka din tha to Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) aain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baain janib beth gaeen, jabkey Umme- Hani (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke daain janib thin, pas londi bartan mein mashrub laee aur usey aap ki khidmat mein pesh kya, aapney us se nosh farmaya , uskey baad aapney bartan Umme- Hani ko diya to unhoney us se piya phir unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine to roza tod liya hai, main to rozey se thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''kya tum koi qaza dey rahi thin ?'' unhoney kaha : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar nafli tha to phir tumharey liye nuqsandeh nahin .'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Darmi . Ahmed aur Tirmizi ki eik riwayat isi tarah hai aur is mein hai : unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main to roze se thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nafli roze daar apney nafs ka ameer hai, wo agar chahey to rakhey (yani pura karey) aur agar chahey to iftaar kar ley.''"
2080,"Hazrat Imam Zohri, Urwa se aur wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) roza se thin, hamen khana pesh kya gaya to hamen uski khahish hui to ham ne is mein se kha liya , Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham dono roza se thin, hamen khana pesh kya gaya to hamen uski khahish hui to ham ne is mein se kha liya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski jagah kisi aur din se qaza karo.'' Tirmizi aur unhoney haafizon ki jamaat ka zikr kya, unhoney Zohri an (an) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki sanad se mursal riwayat kya hai aur unhoney is mein Urwa ka zikr nahin kya, aur yehi ziyada sahih hai, aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne usey Urwa ke azad karda ghulam zameel an (an) Urwa an (an) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki sanad se riwayat kya hai."
2081,"Hazrat Umme-Umaara bint Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke yahan tashrif laye to unhoney aap ke liye khana mangwaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''khaao.'' unhoney arz kya, main roze se hun, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab roze daar ke paas khaya jaey to farishtey uskey liye maghfirat talab kartey rehtey hain yahan tak ke khaney waley (khaney sey) farigh ho jatey hain.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
2082,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap nashta kar rahey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Bilal! nashta kar lo.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main roze se hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham apna rizq kha rahey hain jabkey Bilal ka umda rizq jannat mein hai, Bilal! kya tumhen malum hai ke jab roze daar ke paas khaya jaey to uski haddiyan tasbih bayan karti hain aur farishtey uskey liye maghfirat talab kartey hain.''"
2083,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey ki taaq raaton mein shabe- qadr talash karo.'' Bukhari ."
2084,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chand Sahaba ko shabe-qadr b-haalate-khuwab Ramazan ke aakhiri hafte (saat dinon) mein dikhai gaee, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main dekhta hun ke tumharey khuwab aakhiri hafte mein muttafiq w muwaafiq hain, pas jo shakhs usey talash karna chahey to wo usey aakhiri haftey hain talash karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2085,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is (shabe-qadr) ko Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo, shabe-qadr baqi rehney wali naween raat, saatwin raat, paanchwin raat (yani ikkeeswin, teiswin aur pachchiswin raat ( mein hai.'' Bukhari ."
2086,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ramazan ke pehley ashrey mein aetikaf kya, phir aapney darmiyaney ashrey main eik chhotey se khemey mein aetikaf kya, phir aapney apna sar bahar nikal kar farmaya : ''maine pehla ashra aetikaf kya, main us raat ko talash karna chahta tha, phir maine darmiyaney ashrey ka aetikaf kya, phir merey paas farishta aaya to mujhey kaha gaya ke wo aakhiri ashrey mein hai, jo shakhs merey sath aetikaf karna chahey to wo aakhiri ashra aetikaf karey, mujhey ye raat dikhai gaee thi, phir mujhey bhula di gaee, maine uski subh khud ko keechad mein sajda kartey huey dekha hai, usey aakhiri ashrey mein talash karo aur usey her taaq raat mein talash karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, us raat barish hui, masjid ki chhat shaakhon se bani hui thi wo tapakney lagi, meri aakhon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ki peshani par keechad ka nishan tha aur ye ikkeeswin ki raat (yani ikkeeswin taareekh) thi. muttafaq aleh. maana ke lihaz se Bukhari, Muslim, is par muttafiq aur فقیل لی انھا فی العشر الا واخر tak Muslim ke alfaz hain, jabke baqi sahih Bukhari ke alfaz hain."
2087,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : teisween raat. rawahu Muslim ."
2088,"Hazrat Zarr bin Habish bayan kartey hain, maine Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ke bhai ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke jo shakhs pura saal tahajjud padhega wo shabe-qadr pa lega, to unhoney farmaya : Allah is par rehem farmaai unhoney ye irada kya ke log is par hi aitimad na kar lein, halanke unhen malum hai ke wo (shabe-qadr ( Ramazan mein hai aur aakhiri ashrey mein hai aur wo sattaaiswin raat hai, phir unhoney inshaAllah kahey baghair qism utha kar kaha wo sattaaiswin shab hai, maine kaha : abu-Munzir! aap ye kaisey kehtey hain? unhoney farmaya : uski alamat ya nishani ki bina par jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen batai thi ke us roz Suraj tulu hoga to uski shuaaein nahin hongi. rawahu Muslim ."
2089,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis qadr aakhiri ashrey mein (ibadat w sakhawat karney ki) koshish kartey they wo uskey ilawa kisi aur waqt nahin kartey they. rawahu Muslim ."
2090,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab aakhiri ashra shuru ho jata to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ibadat ke liye) kamar basta ho jatey, shab bedaari farmatey aur apney ehle khana ko bhi bedaar rakhtey they. muttafaq aleh."
2091,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey bataeyn agar main jaan lun ke kon si raat shabe-qadr hai to main is mein kya dua karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho : aey Allah ! be-shak to darguzar farmanewala hai, darguzar ko pasand farmata hai pas mujh se bhi darguzar farma.'' Ahmed, ibne-Maja, Tirmizi, aur unhoney usey sahih qarar diya hai."
2092,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' shabe-qadr ko ikkeeswin ya teiswin ya pachcheeswin ya sattaaiswin ya unteeswin raat mein talash karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
2093,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shabe-qadr ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo purey Ramazan mein hai.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney farmaya : Sufiyan aur Shoba ne Abu-Is'haq ki sanad se ibne-Umar se moquf riwayat kya hai."
2094,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Unais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! main apney jangal mein rehta hun, aur main alhamdulillah wahin Namaz padhta hun, aap mujhey eik raat ke mutalliq hukm farmaain ke main us raat us masjid mein qiyam karun, aapney farmaya : ''teiswin raat ko qiyam kar.'' unke bete se puchha gaya, aap ke walid kaisey kya kartey they? unhoney bataya : jab aap Asr padh letey to masjid mein dakhil ho jatey aur phir aap kisi hajat ke liye wahan se na nikaltey yahan tak ke namaze-Fajr padh letey, jab Fajr padh letey to wo masjid ke darwazey par apni sawari paatey aur is par Sawar ho kar apney jangal mein aa jatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2095,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) shabe-qadr ke mutalliq hamen bataaney ke liye tashrif laye to do musalman baham (aapas mein) jhagad rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen shabe-qadr ke mutalliq bataaney ke liye aaya tha, lekin falan aur falan baham (aapas mein) jhagad padey to wo mujh se utha li gaee aur mumkin hai ke tumharey liye behtar ho, lihaza tum usey ikkeeswin, teisween aur pachchiswin raat mein talash karo.'' Bukhari ."
2096,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab shabe-qadr hoti hai to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) farishton ki jamaat mein tashrif latey hain to wo Allah azz-w-jall ke zikr mein masroof her khadey bethey shakhs par rehmat bhejtey hain, jab unki eid ka din hota hai to Allah Taala unki wajeh se apney farishton par fakhr kartey huey farmata hai : merey farishto! us mazdoor ki kya jaza honi chahiye jo apna kaam pura karta hai? wo arz kartey hain, parwardigar ! uski jaza ye hai ke usey pura pura badla diya jaey, Allah Taala farmata hai : merey farishto ! merey bandon aur meri laundiyon ne meri taraf se un par aaid fareezey ko pura kar diya phir wo duayen pukartey huey nikley hain, mujhey meri izzat w jalal , merey karam w uloo aur apney buland maqam ki qism ! main unki duayen qubul karunga , wo farmata hai : wapis chaley jaao , maine tumhen bakhsh diya aur tumhari khataaon ko nekiyon mein badal diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo us haal mein wapis aatey hain ke unki maghfirat ho chuki hoti hai.'' ."
2097,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri ashrey mein aetikaf kartey rahey yahan tak ke Allah ne unhen faut kar liya , phir aap ki wafat ke baad paak biviyon ne aetikaf kya. muttafaq aleh."
2098,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khair w bhalai mein sab se ziyada sakhi they, aur jab Ramazan mein Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mulaqat kartey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sakhawat badh jati, wo Ramazan ki her raat aap se mulaqat kartey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen Quran sunaya kartey they, jab Jibrael aap se mulaqat kartey to aap khair w bhalai aur sakhawat karney mein khuli hawa (tez raftaar aandhi) se bhi badh kar hotey they. muttafaq aleh."
2099,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko her saal eik martaba Quran sunaya jata tha, aur jis saal aap ki jaan qabz ki gaee us saal do martaba sunaya gaya, aur aap her saal das din aetikaf kya kartey they lekin jis saal aap ki jaan qabz ki gaee us saal aapney bees roz aetikaf farmaya. Bukhari ."
2100,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf farmaya kartey to aap apna sar Mubarak merey qarib kar detey jabkey aap masjid mein hotey they, mein aap ke kanghi kar deti aur aap sirf insani hajat ke tehat hi ghar mein tashrif laya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
2101,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla daryaft kya, maine daure-jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke main masjide-haram main eik raat aetikaf karunga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apni nazar puri karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2102,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ke aakhiri das din mein aetikaf kya kartey they, lekin aapney eik saal aetikaf na kya to phir aainda saal aapney bees roz ka aetikaf kya. rawahu Tirmizi ."
2103,Hazrat Imam Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja ne usey Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai.
2104,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aetikaf karney ka irada farmatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr ada kartey aur phir apney aetikaf ki jagah mein tashrif ley jatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
2105,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haalat aetikaf mein mareez ki iyaadat kar liya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney haal mein chaltey jatey aur rukey baghair uska haal daryaft kar letey. ."
2106,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, aetikaf karney waley ke liye masnoon yehi hai ke wo kisi mareez ki iyaadat karey na janaazey mein shirkat karey, aurat se jima karey na usey galey lagaey aur kisi bahut hi zaroori kaam ke ilawa aetikaf ki jagah se bahar na nikley neez rozey ke baghair aetikaf hai na Jaame masjid ke baghair .''"
2107,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke jab aap aetikaf farmatey to tauba ke sutoon ke peechey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye bistar bicha diya jata ya chaarpai laga di jati. rawahu ibne-Maja .
2108,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aetikaf karney waley ke barey mein farmaya : ''wo gunahon se ruka rehta hai aur tamam nekiyan karney waley ki tarah usey nekiyon ka sawab milta rahta hai.'' (jinko wo pehley kya karta tha).
